rComments: Her lectures are boring and useless. You don't learn anything in this course. Most of the material is just common sense stuff.

Hands-down the most boring professor in all my years of education! Even coffee-addicts are not immune to the boredom. Guest lectures were a bit more entertaining, but the whole class just seems useless and a waste of money. We dont need university/college to teach us how to "blog"! This is the 21st century! We've been blogging since the age of 12!
Not bad. Not great either. You shouldn't have too hard of a time in her class.

Terrible prof. She should really learn how to make powerpoint slides since she repeats the same point 3-4 times in the same slide. Very boring lecturer, if you have trouble sleeping attend her lecture and you'll sleep like a baby. Assignments are stupid... For example: talk about yourself and your family. This isn't grade 3.
bad prof, no effort to make material interesting....  generally dumb
Bad prof, really boring, very vague, don't take this course or anything she teaches.
Never get to know what she really wants! Lectures are quite good though.
Really nice lady, very smart.  I hated the assignments that we had though . . . she isn't very clear on her expectations always
